Goals of this project:
practicing how to display 3D objects
oriented in any way and viewed from any position


viewing proj:

--------
to compile: 
--------
 just enter 'make' to compile

--------
to run:
--------
./main

when log into ssh server make sure to turn on Xming to run program
after compile enter 'main' then it will open new windows
w - go forward
s - go backward
a - go to left
d - go to right

use mouse to turn a point of view
home key to reset the position and camera view

./main 1000 800

here 
  1000 is width; 800 is height

bug: robot will turn around when the point of view turns
but it will not follow or it will not alway at the back of the camera position
